Batteries don't discharge by leaking to ground.  they discharge by
leaking
between their terminals. 
-------------------- Clip ------------------
Dirty batteries are on a self destruct cycle.
The battery needs to be clean and the acid on the outside needs to be
neutralized with baking soda.

